    <item>
      <title>Split() function for Microsoft MSSQL</title>
      <link>http://blog2.snowfrog.net/2014/01/07/split-function-for-microsoft-mssql/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://blog2.snowfrog.net/2014/01/07/split-function-for-microsoft-mssql/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Microsoft MSSQL doesn&amp;rsquo;t have a split() function (like in &lt;a href=&#34;http://ruby-doc.org/core-1.9.3/String.html#method-i-split&#34;&gt;Ruby&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://perldoc.perl.org/functions/split.html&#34;&gt;Perl&lt;/a&gt;), so here&amp;rsquo;s one I wrote.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s different from the other MSSQL split() functions out there on the intertubes in that it accepts a @pos parameter that specifies which split item to return - easier than trying to tangle with tables inside a calling function when you want the n&amp;rsquo;th split item.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #202020&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;FUNCTION&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;[dbo].[split]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;varchar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;MAX&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;delimiter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;CHAR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@pos&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;RETURNS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;varchar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;255&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;BEGIN&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;DECLARE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #24909d&#34;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt; 
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;CHARINDEX(@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;delimiter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@string),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; 
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;WHILE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;LEN(@string)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;BEGIN&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; 
            &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;LEN(@string)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; 

        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@pos&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;RETURN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SUBSTRING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(@string,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; 
        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;CHARINDEX(@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;delimiter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@string,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; 

    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;END&lt;/span&gt; 
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;RETURN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #999999; font-style: italic&#34;&gt;-- not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;END&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;dbo.split(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aa,bb,cc&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;dbo.split(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aa,bb,cc&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;dbo.split(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aa,bb,cc&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;dbo.split(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aa,bb,cc&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;dbo.split(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;aa,bb,cc&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;,&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color: #999999; font-style: italic&#34;&gt;--------------&lt;/span&gt;

                   &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;zero&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #3677a9&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #6ab825; font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;row&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;(s)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #d0d0d0&#34;&gt;affected)&lt;/span&gt;
